title: Proposal for a CAKE-SMG farm & Syrup pool
body:
CAKE holders, today we are proposing a new Syrup Pool & farm with SMG token. 

Smaugs NFT: 

Smaugs NFT is a marketplace where you can sell all of its assets in the digital world. Smaugs marketplace is working on the Binance smart chain and completely decentralized. You can turn your assets in the digital world into NFT tokens using the Smaugs NFT marketplace and earn a lot of different gifts.

Smaugs Battle: is a blockchain-based battle game played online on the Binance smart chain network. It will be released on google play store next month. Stay tuned
choices: We want to earn more SMG tokens!
We don't want to earn more SMG tokens!
